		{"id":"hitl-summary","type":"text","text":"## ⚑ HITL Checkpoints (8 Total)\n\n1️⃣ Inbox triage\n2️⃣ Strategy crystallization\n3️⃣ Decision recording\n4️⃣ Issue confirmation\n5️⃣ PR approval\n6️⃣ Merge decision\n7️⃣ Doc updates\n8️⃣ Synthesis review","x":-800,"y":900,"width":280,"height":180},
		{"id":"data-flow","type":"text","text":"## 📦 Data Repositories\n\nvault/inbox/ → Signal capture\nvault/daily/ → Context & reference\nvault/strategy/ → Thinking & decisions\nvault/decisions/ → Decision records\nproject/DECISIONS.md → Agent constraints\nGitHub Issues → Implementation backlog\nPull Requests → Implementation tracking","x":-450,"y":900,"width":350,"height":200},
		{"id":"principles","type":"text","text":"## 🎯 Key Principles\n\n✓ Skills are reusable templates\n✓ HITL points are leverage\n✓ Humans review outputs (not write from scratch)\n✓ Feedback loops enable refinement\n✓ Always-on guards protect quality\n✓ Context chains preserve knowledge","x":100,"y":900,"width":320,"height":200},
